,Recommended,214340,11809340,"Posted: 21 August, 2014",all,S_C_S_I,"Deponia is a point-and-click adventure reminiscent of the infamous Monkey Island series. The game is part of a trilogy (Deponia -> Chaos On Deponia -> Goodbye Deponia). You play Rufus, the archetypical anti-hero whose bad jokes are only matched by his failed attempts to leave his junk covered planet Deponia. While the story unfolds you will be busy searching that single missing item to progress, creating thought provoking item combinations and solving mind boggling puzzles. All-in-all an entertaining game, but certainly not up to par with Monkey Island. Good enough to start playing Chaos On Deponia. :)Score: 7/10Pro:+ nice cartoonish look & feel+ entertaining story+ decent voice acting+ absurd humourContra:- bad humour- clicking feels so 1990... ;)"
